<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="tolerate-vt">tolerate <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'tɒləreɪt/    美 /'tɑːləreɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-put-up-with">1.★ <strong>容忍；忍受 (put up with)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Those who know how to tolerate others can naturally lead a happy life. 
那些懂得容忍他人的人自然可以过得幸福。</p></div></div>